{"ts":"2026-06-26T00:26:19.998Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_end","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Exploring the Codebase**\n\nI'm now diving into the codebase! I'm seeing a well-structured project with specific paths like `app/why-gff-ai/garage-foundry-factory/page.tsx`, `app/platforms/page.tsx`, `app/platforms/foundry/page.tsx`, and `app/platforms/marketplace/page.tsx`. This suggests a clear organization focused on different platform areas and explanations.\n\n\n**Updating the Capabilities List**\n\nI'm now cross-referencing the codebase with the capabilities list from the command grid. I'm noting the discrepancies and planning an update to `app/capabilities/page.tsx`. This includes making sure all 11 core capabilities from the grid are represented, which necessitates an update to the current list of 5 capabilities. Next I will refactor `app/capabilities/page.tsx` for a better user experience.\n\n\n**Defining the UI Elements**\n\nI'm now zeroing in on the UI for `app/capabilities/page.tsx`, deciding on the specific elements to include. It has to feature an interactive Command Grid of all eleven capabilities with details pages, a layered Enterprise AI Stack visualization, Agent Factory/Knowledge Graph Factory blocks, and a Garage-to-Factory progression. I'm imagining a timeline or grid to represent the shift from incubation to full-scale operations.\n\n\n**Refining the Design**\n\nI'm now fully immersed in the design phase for `app/capabilities/page.tsx`, and I'm realizing this directly aligns with GFF's \"Garage, Foundry, Factory\" concept. I'm focusing on premium, modern styling, responsive layouts, and custom UI patterns. I'm leveraging `lucide-react` and `react-icons` for icons, considering inline SVGs for maximum control. I'm also preparing to create subpages for enhanced organization.\n\n\n**Designing the Template**\n\nI'm now outlining subpages, focusing on a shared, data-driven template for all of them. This is intended to ensure code quality and consistent styling. I want the subpages to be fully populated with custom contents. This will involve components for hero visuals, use-case grids, and architecture diagrams, among other features. The plan is to create `app/capabilities/[slug]/page.tsx`.\n\n\n**Mapping the Subpages**\n\nI'm now determining explicit App Router directories and pages for each subpage within `/capabilities/`. I'm going with `/capabilities/strategy/page.tsx`, `/capabilities/engineering/page.tsx`, and so on, for all eleven capabilities. This will maintain App Router explicit routing. To avoid code duplication, I'll create a reusable client component, `CapabilitySubpageFamily.tsx`, and then use small wrapper pages to pass tailored data to this shared component. This will allow for elegant and maintainable code.\n\n\n**Crafting the Component**\n\nI'm now diving into the architecture for `CapabilitySubpageFamily.tsx`, focusing on its specific components. I've broken it down into `InnerPageShell` for overall structure and `InnerPageHero` for header information. I plan for a `Use-Case Grid` showcasing enterprise use cases, and an `Interactive Architecture Diagram` visualizing the layers of this capability. I'm designing a `Delivery Model Panel` to show GFF's approach and a `Business Outcomes Section` for tangible results. All of this is aimed at making the subpages easy to maintain!\n\n\n**Visualizing the Components**\n\nI'm now integrating related platforms and industry links into the capabilities grid, including premium CTAs. I'm focusing on crafting unique SVG visualizations for the interactive stack, aiming for visually engaging inline SVG components to represent each capability's hero section, and for enhanced clarity. I'm moving toward an advanced sketch of `CapabilitySubpageFamily.tsx`.\n\nI'm starting to sketch out what the `InnerPageShell` and the `InnerPageHero` will look like.\n\n\n**Defining the Architecture**\n\nI'm now focusing on a plan for dynamic content in each capability subpage, considering custom React components or render props. The goal is a highly customized and premium feel. To ensure scalability, I'm documenting all required imports, which include React, `lucide-react`, and various inner-page components. I'm also planning the `app/capabilities/page.tsx` landing page, starting with a hero section featuring a technical architecture category. I'm prioritizing the layout and elements of the home page. I will focus on an \"Interactive Enterprise AI Stack Layer Visualizer\".\n\n\n**Visualizing the Architecture**\n\nI'm now diving into the specifics of the interactive Enterprise AI Stack visualizer on the landing page. I'm choosing between a vertical 3D-angled or flat stacked layout to display the layers. I'm focusing on user interaction, where each layer reveals detailed specifications upon selection. Key layers include the Experience Layer (unified agent interface), Agentic AI Layer (multi-agent orchestration), Knowledge Graph Layer (semantic mapping), Data and Integration Layer (real-time syncing), Governance Layer (compliance), and Managed AI Operations Layer (performance). I'm also ensuring a responsive Capability Command Grid showcases the eleven capabilities.\n\n\n**Drafting the Design**\n\nI'm now drafting the Garage-to-Factory Progression graphic, the Agent Factory & Knowledge Graph Factory visual grid, and incorporating related platform quick cards with premium CTAs. I'm prioritizing sophisticated visual effects for the components: Tailwind hover effects, gradients, glowing borders, and clean fonts. I'm investigating `components/inner-pages/AnimatedBackgroundGrid.tsx` for possible implementation.\n\n\n"}}
{"ts":"2026-06-26T00:26:20.010Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"tool","toolName":"editor","toolCallId":"7n3lgnin","input":{"path":"/Users/ayushbansal/Documents/GitHub/hirezapp_landing_page/app/capabilities/page.tsx","new_text":"\"use client\";\n\nimport React, { useState } from \"react\";\nimport InnerPageShell from \"@/components/inner-pages/InnerPageShell\";\nimport InnerPageHero from \"@/components/inner-pages/InnerPageHero\";\nimport PremiumCTA from \"@/components/inner-pages/PremiumCTA\";\nimport { \n  Network, \n  Cpu, \n  Shield, \n  Database, \n  Workflow, \n  Activity, \n  GraduationCap, \n  Layers, \n  Settings, \n  FlaskConical, \n  Compass, \n  Wrench,\n  CheckCircle2,\n  ArrowRight,\n  TrendingUp,\n  FileCode,\n  Zap,\n  Lock,\n  GitBranch\n} from \"lucide-react\";\n\n// Types\ninterface CapabilityNode {\n  id: string;\n  title: string;\n  href: string;\n  shortDesc: string;\n  tag: string;\n  icon: React.ReactNode;\n  color: string;\n}\n\ninterface StackLayer {\n  id: string;\n  name: string;\n  tech: string[];\n  specs: string[];\n  desc: string;\n}\n\nexport default function CapabilitiesPage() {\n  const [activeLayer, setActiveLayer] = useState<string>(\"agentic\");\n\n  // Capabilities directory definitions\n  const capabilities: CapabilityNode[] = [\n    {\n      id: \"strategy\",\n      title: \"AI Strategy & Roadmap\",\n      href: \"/capabilities/strategy\",\n      shortDesc: \"Architect custom readiness blueprints, feasibility studies, and ROI simulations aligned with executive strategy.\",\n      tag: \"INCEPTION\",\n      icon: <Compass className=\"w-5 h-5 text-[#E4000F]\" />,\n      color: \"#E4000F\"\n    },\n    {\n      id: \"engineering\",\n      title: \"Core AI Engineering\",\n      href: \"/capabilities/engineering\",\n      shortDesc: \"Build and scale custom foundation networks, low-latency API architectures, and localized LLM deployments.\",\n      tag: \"ENGINEERING\",\n      icon: <Wrench className=\"w-5 h-5 text-[#009DFF]\" />,\n      color: \"#009DFF\"\n    },\n    {\n      id: \"agents\",\n      title: \"Autonomous Agents\",\n      href: \"/capabilities/agents\",\n      shortDesc: \"Deploy multi-agent orchestrations and goal-directed cognitive loops that run business workflows with high autonomy.\",\n      tag: \"AGENTIC\",\n      icon: <Cpu className=\"w-5 h-5 text-purple-400\" />,\n      color: \"#A855F7\"\n    },\n    {\n      id: \"governance\",\n      title: \"Governance & Compliance\",\n      href: \"/capabilities/governance\",\n      shortDesc: \"Implement continuous safety guardrails, real-time input/output sanitization, PII shielding, and compliance audit logging.\",\n      tag: \"SECURITY\",\n      icon: <Shield className=\"w-5 h-5 text-emerald-400\" />,\n      color: \"#10B981\"\n    },\n    {\n      id: \"data\",\n      title: \"Enterprise Data & Vector DB\",\n      href: \"/capabilities/data\",\n      shortDesc: \"Design real-time CDC sync, hybrid vector database partitioning, and high-volume unstructured semantic indexing.\",\n      tag: \"DATA\",\n      icon: <Database className=\"w-5 h-5 text-amber-400\" />,\n      color: \"#F59E0B\"\n    },\n    {\n      id: \"labs\",\n      title: \"Labs & Prototyping\",\n      href: \"/capabilities/labs\",\n      shortDesc: \"Rapid incubation sandbox designed to stress-test frontier models, model fine-tuning, and prompt optimization loops.\",\n      tag: \"EXPERIMENT\",\n      icon: <FlaskConical className=\"w-5 h-5 text-pink-400\" />,\n      color: \"#EC4899\"\n    },\n    {\n      id: \"operations\",\n      title: \"AI Operations & Monitoring\",\n      href: \"/capabilities/operations\",\n      shortDesc: \"Deploy automated operational monitors tracking semantic latency, cost anomalies, token consumption, and fallback systems.\",\n      tag: \"TELEMETRY\",\n      icon: <Activity className=\"w-5 h-5 text-cyan-400\" />,\n      color: \"#06B6D4\"\n    },\n    {\n      id: \"twins\",\n      title: \"Cognitive Digital Twins\",\n      href: \"/capabilities/twins\",\n      shortDesc: \"Model complex, multi-variable business assets and processes inside high-fidelity digital replicas for optimization.\",\n      tag: \"SIMULATION\",\n      icon: <Layers className=\"w-5 h-5 text-indigo-400\" />,\n      color: \"#6366F1\"\n    },\n    {\n      id: \"universities\",\n      title: \"AI Enablement & Academics\",\n      href: \"/capabilities/universities\",\n      shortDesc: \"Upskill internal developers and empower strategic leaders with corporate-grade technical AI enablement academies.\",\n      tag: \"ENABLEMENT\",\n      icon: <GraduationCap className=\"w-5 h-5 text-teal-400\" />,\n      color: \"#14B8A6\"\n    },\n    {\n      id: \"knowledge-graph\",\n      title: \"Semantic Knowledge Graphs\",\n      href: \"/capabilities/knowledge-graph\",\n      shortDesc: \"Engineer rich context layers coupling structured entity graphs with high-dimensional vector search index databases.\",\n      tag: \"COGNITIVE\",\n      icon: <Network className=\"w-5 h-5 text-violet-400\" />,\n      color: \"#8B5CF6\"\n    },\n    {\n      id: \"managed-services\",\n      title: \"Managed AI Services\",\n      href: \"/capabilities/managed-services\",\n      shortDesc: \"End-to-end management of custom models and operational stacks with 24/7 SLA monitoring, optimization, and upgrades.\",\n      tag: \"OPERATIONS\",\n      icon: <Settings className=\"w-5 h-5 text-[#E4000F]\" />,\n      color: \"#E4000F\"\n    }\n  ];\n\n  // Enterprise Stack definitions\n  const stackLayers: StackLayer[] = [\n    {\n      id: \"experience\",\n      name: \"Experience Layer\",\n      desc: \"High-end, customizable client interaction surfaces, web chat interfaces, custom enterprise portal dashboards, and API endpoints delivering sub-second response times.\",\n      tech: [\"Next.js React\", \"Tailwind CSS\", \"WebSockets\", \"gRPC Gateway\"],\n      specs: [\"Sub-50ms render loop\", \"Universal Mobile Viewports\", \"Dynamic Widget injection\"]\n    },\n    {\n      id: \"agentic\",\n      name: \"Agentic AI Layer\",\n      desc: \"Goal-directed multi-agent frameworks executing complex reasoning. Routes workflows to specialized agents, executes custom tool integrations, and implements self-correction loops.\",\n      tech: [\"GFF Orchestrator\", \"LangGraph Custom\", \"Auto-correction loops\", \"Pydantic State Engine\"],\n      specs: [\"Asynchronous worker scaling\", \"State isolation sandbox\", \"Dynamic tool execution (0-day latency)\"]\n    },\n    {\n      id: \"knowledge\",\n      name: \"Knowledge Graph Layer\",\n      desc: \"The semantic bridge indexing relational structures alongside unstructured models. Powers hybrid Search, entity-relation navigation, and multi-hop contextual synthesis.\",\n      tech: [\"Neo4j Graph Database\", \"pgvector Postgres\", \"Custom entity-extractors\", \"Semantic cache indexing\"],\n      specs: [\"10M+ Entity node support\", \"Multi-hop reasoning (under 120ms)\", \"Deterministic lineage tracking\"]\n    },\n    {\n      id: \"data\",\n      name: \"Data and Integration Layer\",\n      desc: \"Enterprise data integration pipelines. Syncs transactional data in real-time, processes multi-modal documents, and maintains active memory vectors.\",\n      tech: [\"Apache Kafka\", \"Real-time CDC Pipelines\", \"Chunking pipeline runners\", \"Azure/AWS Gateway sync\"],\n      specs: [\"10k+ document chunks/sec\", \"Zero data retention options\", \"TLS 1.3 encrypted data-in-transit\"]\n    },\n    {\n      id: \"governance\",\n      name: \"Governance & Guardrail Layer\",\n      desc: \"Dual-directional safety firewall intercepting prompts and outputs. Detects and sanitizes PII data leaks, filters toxic prompts, and guarantees model alignment.\",\n      tech: [\"GFF Shield Gateway\", \"Continuous SOC2 policy validator\", \"Anonymization engines\", \"Llama Guard 3 custom\"],\n      specs: [\"Inbound/outbound latency <12ms\", \"PII scrubbing with 99.9% recall\", \"Compliance audit logs (immutable)\"]\n    },\n    {\n      id: \"operations\",\n      name: \"Managed AI Operations (AIOps)\",\n      desc: \"Telemetry, logging, and operation pipeline. Monitors cost curves, checks execution health across clusters, and triggers failover models.\",\n      tech: [\"Prometheus metrics\", \"Grafana customized boards\", \"Continuous tuning cron-jobs\", \"GFF Telemetry engine\"],\n      specs: [\"Telemetry collection <5ms\", \"Automated model failover\", \"Cost anomaly detection engines\"]\n    }\n  ];\n\n  const activeLayerData = stackLayers.find(l => l.id === activeLayer) || stackLayers[1];\n\n  return (\n    <InnerPageShell>\n      {/* Premium Hero */}\n      <InnerPageHero\n        category=\"Architecture & Systems\"\n        title=\"Technical Capabilities\"\n        highlightedWord=\"Capabilities\"\n        description=\"GFF AI engineers resilient, precise, and secure enterprise-grade systems architectures designed to elevate core business operations with autonomous intelligence.\"\n        breadcrumbs={[\n          { label: \"Home\", href: \"/\" },\n          { label: \"Capabilities\" }\n        ]}\n      />\n\n      {/* SECTION 1: INTERACTIVE ENTERPRISE AI STACK */}\n      <section className=\"relative w-full px-6 lg:px-16 pb-24\">\n        <div className=\"max-w-[1795px] mx-auto\">\n          <div className=\"text-center max-w-[800px] mx-auto mb-16\">\n            <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono tracking-[0.2em] text-[#009DFF] uppercase font-bold\">\n              THE STRUCTURAL FABRIC\n            </span>\n            <h2 className=\"text-[28px] sm:text-[38px] font-bold text-white tracking-tight mt-2\">\n              Enterprise AI Stack Architecture\n            </h2>\n            <p className=\"mt-4 text-[14.5px] text-white/60 font-light leading-[1.6]\">\n              A production-proven model comprising six unified layers. Click or hover any stack layer on the blueprint to inspect core components and compliance-driven engineering.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n\n          <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center\">\n            {/* Interactive SVG Layer stack */}\n            <div className=\"lg:col-span-7 flex flex-col justify-center items-center\">\n              <div className=\"w-full max-w-[550px] aspect-[4/3] relative\">\n                <svg className=\"w-full h-full\" viewBox=\"0 0 600 480\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n                  {/* Pipes & Flow Lines */}\n                  <path d=\"M120 40 L120 440 M480 40 L480 440\" stroke=\"rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03)\" strokeWidth=\"2\" strokeDasharray=\"5 10\" />\n                  <path d=\"M300 40 L300 440\" stroke=\"url(#stackPipeGlow)\" strokeWidth=\"1.5\" strokeDasharray=\"10 8\" />\n\n                  {/* 6 Layers of Stack */}\n                  {[\n                    { id: \"experience\", y: 40, label: \"Experience Layer\", subtitle: \"Interfaces, Chat Overlays & APIs\", color: \"#E4000F\" },\n                    { id: \"agentic\", y: 105, label: \"Agentic AI Layer\", subtitle: \"Dynamic Reasoning & Multi-Agent Loops\", color: \"url(#brandGlow)\" },\n                    { id: \"knowledge\", y: 170, label: \"Knowledge Graph Layer\", subtitle: \"Semantic Entities & Vector Indexes\", color: \"#8B5CF6\" },\n                    { id: \"data\", y: 235, label: \"Data and Integration Layer\", subtitle: \"Real-time CDC, Chunking & DB Gateways\", color: \"#F59E0B\" },\n                    { id: \"governance\", y: 300, label: \"Governance & Guardrail Layer\", subtitle: \"Sanitization Filters & Threat Monitors\", color: \"#10B981\" },\n                    { id: \"operations\", y: 365, label: \"Managed AI Operations (AIOps)\", subtitle: \"Continuous Fine-tuning & Telemetry\", color: \"#009DFF\" }\n                  ].map((layer, index) => {\n                    const isSelected = activeLayer === layer.id;\n                    return (\n                      <g \n                        key={layer.id} \n                        onClick={() => setActiveLayer(layer.id)}\n                        className=\"cursor-pointer group select-none\"\n                      >\n                        {/* Layer card with isometric offset effect */}\n                        <rect \n                          x=\"50\" \n                          y={layer.y} \n                          width=\"500\" \n                          height=\"50\" \n                          rx=\"12\" \n                          fill={isSelected ? \"rgba(10, 10, 12, 0.95)\" : \"rgba(3, 3, 4, 0.6)\"}\n                          stroke={isSelected ? layer.color : \"rgba(255,255,255,0.06)\"}\n                          strokeWidth={isSelected ? \"2\" : \"1.2\"} \n                          className=\"transition-all duration-300 group-hover:stroke-white/30\"\n                        />\n                        \n                        {/* Glow background when selected */}\n                        {isSelected && (\n                          <rect \n                            x=\"48\" \n                            y={layer.y - 2} \n                            width=\"504\" \n                            height=\"54\" \n                            rx=\"14\" \n                            stroke={layer.color} \n                            strokeWidth=\"1.5\" \n                            className=\"opacity-40 blur-[4px] pointer-events-none\"\n                          />\n                        )}\n\n                        {/* Text and layer numbering */}\n                        <text x=\"75\" y={layer.y + 24} fill={isSelected ? \"#FFF\" : \"rgba(255,255,255,0.4)\"} fontSize=\"11\" fontWeight=\"bold\" fontFamily=\"monospace\">\n                          {`0${index + 1}`}\n                        </text>\n\n                        <text x=\"110\" y={layer.y + 23} fill={isSelected ? \"#FFF\" : \"rgba(255,255,255,0.85)\"} fontSize=\"13.5\" fontWeight=\"600\" className=\"transition-colors duration-300\">\n                          {layer.label}\n                        </text>\n\n                        <text x=\"110\" y={layer.y + 39} fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.4)\" fontSize=\"10.5\" fontWeight=\"light\" className=\"transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:fill-white/60\">\n                          {layer.subtitle}\n                        </text>\n\n                        {/* Indicator Circle */}\n                        <circle \n                          cx=\"510\" \n                          cy={layer.y + 25} \n                          r={isSelected ? \"5\" : \"4\"} \n                          fill={isSelected ? layer.color : \"rgba(255,255,255,0.15)\"} \n                          className=\"transition-all duration-300 group-hover:fill-white/40\"\n                        />\n                      </g>\n                    );\n                  })}\n\n                  <defs>\n                    <linearGradient id=\"brandGlow\" x1=\"0\" y1=\"0\" x2=\"500\" y2=\"0\" gradientUnits=\"userSpaceOnUse\">\n                      <stop stopColor=\"#E4000F\" />\n                      <stop offset=\"1\" stopColor=\"#009DFF\" />\n                    </linearGradient>\n                    <linearGradient id=\"stackPipeGlow\" x1=\"0\" y1=\"0\" x2=\"0\" y2=\"440\" gradientUnits=\"userSpaceOnUse\">\n                      <stop stopColor=\"#E4000F\" />\n                      <stop offset=\"0.5\" stopColor=\"#8B5CF6\" />\n                      <stop offset=\"1\" stopColor=\"#009DFF\" />\n                    </linearGradient>\n                  </defs>\n                </svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Spec readout display */}\n            <div className=\"lg:col-span-5 flex flex-col justify-between h-full bg-[#030304]/60 backdrop-blur-[16px] border border-white/5 rounded-[24px] p-8 min-h-[360px]\">\n              <div>\n                <div className=\"flex items-center gap-3\">\n                  <span className=\"px-2.5 py-0.5 text-[9px] font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#009DFF] bg-[#009DFF]/5 border border-[#009DFF]/20 rounded-full\">\n                    SYSTEM COMPONENT INSPECTOR\n                  </span>\n                </div>\n                <h3 className=\"text-[22px] font-bold text-white tracking-tight mt-3\">\n                  {activeLayerData.name}\n                </h3>\n                <p className=\"mt-4 text-[13.5px] leading-[1.6] text-white/60 font-light\">\n                  {activeLayerData.desc}\n                </p>\n\n                <div className=\"mt-6\">\n                  <h4 className=\"text-[11px] font-mono uppercase text-white/40 tracking-wider\">\n                    Core Technical Specifications\n                  </h4>\n                  <ul className=\"mt-3 space-y-2\">\n                    {activeLayerData.specs.map((spec, idx) => (\n                      <li key={idx} className=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-[12.5px] font-light text-white/80\">\n                        <CheckCircle2 className=\"w-4 h-4 text-[#009DFF] shrink-0 mt-0.5\" />\n                        <span>{spec}</span>\n                      </li>\n                    ))}\n                  </ul>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              <div className=\"mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-white/5\">\n                <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono uppercase text-white/30 tracking-wider\">\n                  Approved Framework Integration\n                </span>\n                <div className=\"mt-2.5 flex flex-wrap gap-1.5\">\n                  {activeLayerData.tech.map((t, i) => (\n                    <span key={i} className=\"px-2 py-0.5 rounded-[4px] bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-[10.5px] font-mono text-white/70\">\n                      {t}\n                    </span>\n                  ))}\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      {/* SECTION 2: CAPABILITY COMMAND GRID */}\n      <section className=\"relative w-full px-6 lg:px-16 pb-24 border-t border-white/5 pt-20\">\n        <div className=\"max-w-[1795px] mx-auto\">\n          <div className=\"text-center max-w-[800px] mx-auto mb-16\">\n            <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono tracking-[0.2em] text-[#E4000F] uppercase font-bold\">\n              THE COMMAND MATRIX\n            </span>\n            <h2 className=\"text-[28px] sm:text-[38px] font-bold text-white tracking-tight mt-2\">\n              Capabilities Command Grid\n            </h2>\n            <p className=\"mt-4 text-[14.5px] text-white/60 font-light leading-[1.6]\">\n              Explore our exhaustive deep-dives covering each technical competence vector. Select a card below to inspect architecture configurations and technical specifications.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n\n          <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 xl:grid-cols-4 gap-6\">\n            {capabilities.map((cap) => (\n              <a \n                key={cap.id} \n                href={cap.href}\n                className=\"group relative flex flex-col justify-between p-6 rounded-[24px] border border-white/5 bg-[#030304]/40 backdrop-blur-[8px] hover:border-white/12 hover:bg-[#070709]/80 transition-all duration-300\"\n              >\n                {/* Subtle top left cross */}\n                <div className=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-3 h-3 border-t border-l border-white/10 rounded-tl-[24px]\" />\n                \n                <div>\n                  <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between\">\n                    <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono tracking-widest text-white/40 group-hover:text-[#009DFF] transition-colors uppercase font-semibold\">\n                      {cap.tag}\n                    </span>\n                    <div className=\"p-1.5 rounded-lg bg-white/5 border border-white/10\">\n                      {cap.icon}\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                  \n                  <h3 className=\"text-[17px] font-semibold text-white tracking-tight mt-4 group-hover:text-white transition-colors\">\n                    {cap.title}\n                  </h3>\n                  \n                  <p className=\"mt-2.5 text-[12.5px] leading-[1.5] text-white/50 font-light group-hover:text-white/70 transition-colors\">\n                    {cap.shortDesc}\n                  </p>\n                </div>\n\n                <div className=\"mt-6 pt-4 border-t border-white/5 flex items-center justify-between text-[11px] font-mono tracking-wider text-[#009DFF] group-hover:text-white transition-all\">\n                  <span>INSPECT DEEP-DIVE</span>\n                  <ArrowRight className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 group-hover:translate-x-1.5 transition-transform\" />\n                </div>\n              </a>\n            ))}\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      {/* SECTION 3: AGENT FACTORY & KNOWLEDGE GRAPH FACTORY */}\n      <section className=\"relative w-full px-6 lg:px-16 pb-24 border-t border-white/5 pt-20\">\n        <div className=\"max-w-[1795px] mx-auto\">\n          <div className=\"text-center max-w-[800px] mx-auto mb-16\">\n            <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono tracking-[0.2em] text-[#009DFF] uppercase font-bold\">\n              SCALABLE SYNTHESIS\n            </span>\n            <h2 className=\"text-[28px] sm:text-[38px] font-bold text-white tracking-tight mt-2\">\n              The Agent & Knowledge Graph Factories\n            </h2>\n            <p className=\"mt-4 text-[14.5px] text-white/60 font-light leading-[1.6]\">\n              How we construct custom models and specialized entities. Rather than treating AI as a black box, we build robust factory pipelines to auto-synthesize agents and relational layers.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n\n          <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8\">\n            {/* Agent Factory card */}\n            <div className=\"relative rounded-[24px] border border-white/5 bg-[#030304]/60 backdrop-blur-[12px] p-8 flex flex-col justify-between overflow-hidden\">\n              <div className=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-[40%] aspect-square bg-[#E4000F]/5 rounded-full blur-[40px] pointer-events-none\" />\n              \n              <div>\n                <span className=\"px-3 py-1 text-[9px] font-mono font-bold tracking-[0.1em] text-[#E4000F] border border-[#E4000F]/20 bg-[#E4000F]/5 rounded-full uppercase\">\n                  AGENT FACTORY\n                </span>\n                <h3 className=\"text-[22px] font-bold text-white tracking-tight mt-4\">\n                  Automated Agent Synthesis\n                </h3>\n                <p className=\"mt-3 text-[13.5px] leading-[1.6] text-white/60 font-light\">\n                  Our custom pipeline generates high-fidelity cognitive workers based on declarative task configurations. We map operations, define tooling APIs, validate in safety sandboxes, and compile production agents.\n                </p>\n\n                {/* Agent Factory flow SVG */}\n                <div className=\"mt-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-black/40 flex flex-col gap-3\">\n                  <span className=\"text-[9.5px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase tracking-widest\">Active Pipeline Schema</span>\n                  <div className=\"grid grid-cols-4 gap-2 text-center text-[10px] font-mono\">\n                    <div className=\"p-2 border border-white/5 bg-white/5 rounded-lg flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[70px]\">\n                      <span className=\"text-white/40\">STEP 01</span>\n                      <span className=\"text-white font-semibold\">YAML Schema</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div className=\"p-2 border border-white/5 bg-white/5 rounded-lg flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[70px]\">\n                      <span className=\"text-white/40\">STEP 02</span>\n                      <span className=\"text-white font-semibold\">Tool Binding</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div className=\"p-2 border border-white/5 bg-white/5 rounded-lg flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[70px]\">\n                      <span className=\"text-white/40\">STEP 03</span>\n                      <span className=\"text-[#E4000F] font-semibold\">Evaluation</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div className=\"p-2 border border-white/5 bg-white/5 rounded-lg flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[70px]\">\n                      <span className=\"text-white/40\">STEP 04</span>\n                      <span className=\"text-emerald-400 font-semibold\">Deployment</span>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              <div className=\"mt-6 flex items-center gap-4 text-[11px] font-mono text-white/40\">\n                <span className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><FileCode className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-[#E4000F]\" /> Declarative configs</span>\n                <span className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><Lock className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-[#009DFF]\" /> Sandbox validation</span>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Knowledge Graph Factory card */}\n            <div className=\"relative rounded-[24px] border border-white/5 bg-[#030304]/60 backdrop-blur-[12px] p-8 flex flex-col justify-between overflow-hidden\">\n              <div className=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-[40%] aspect-square bg-[#009DFF]/5 rounded-full blur-[40px] pointer-events-none\" />\n\n              <div>\n                <span className=\"px-3 py-1 text-[9px] font-mono font-bold tracking-[0.1em] text-[#009DFF] border border-[#009DFF]/20 bg-[#009DFF]/5 rounded-full uppercase\">\n                  GRAPH FACTORY\n                </span>\n                <h3 className=\"text-[22px] font-bold text-white tracking-tight mt-4\">\n                  Deterministic Graph Synthesis\n                </h3>\n                <p className=\"mt-3 text-[13.5px] leading-[1.6] text-white/60 font-light\">\n                  Converts dynamic databases and large document libraries into semantic relationships. This eliminates LLM hallucination risk by verifying metadata structures prior to model execution.\n                </p>\n\n                {/* KG Factory flow SVG */}\n                <div className=\"mt-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-black/40 flex flex-col gap-3\">\n                  <span className=\"text-[9.5px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase tracking-widest\">Active Pipeline Schema</span>\n                  <div className=\"grid grid-cols-4 gap-2 text-center text-[10px] font-mono\">\n                    <div className=\"p-2 border border-white/5 bg-white/5 rounded-lg flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[70px]\">\n                      <span className=\"text-white/40\">INPUT</span>\n                      <span className=\"text-white font-semibold\">CDC Data stream</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div className=\"p-2 border border-white/5 bg-white/5 rounded-lg flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[70px]\">\n                      <span className=\"text-white/40\">EXTRACT</span>\n                      <span className=\"text-white font-semibold\">Entity Extraction</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div className=\"p-2 border border-white/5 bg-white/5 rounded-lg flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[70px]\">\n                      <span className=\"text-white/40\">MAP</span>\n                      <span className=\"text-[#009DFF] font-semibold\">Graph Stitching</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div className=\"p-2 border border-white/5 bg-white/5 rounded-lg flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[70px]\">\n                      <span className=\"text-white/40\">INDEX</span>\n                      <span className=\"text-emerald-400 font-semibold\">Hybrid Search</span>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              <div className=\"mt-6 flex items-center gap-4 text-[11px] font-mono text-white/40\">\n                <span className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><GitBranch className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-[#009DFF]\" /> Schema enforcement</span>\n                <span className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><Zap className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-amber-400\" /> Vector database sync</span>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      {/* SECTION 4: GARAGE TO FACTORY LIFE-CYCLE */}\n      <section className=\"relative w-full px-6 lg:px-16 pb-24 border-t border-white/5 pt-20\">\n        <div className=\"max-w-[1795px] mx-auto\">\n          <div className=\"text-center max-w-[800px] mx-auto mb-16\">\n            <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono tracking-[0.2em] text-[#E4000F] uppercase font-bold\">\n              THE DEVELOPMENT LIFECYCLE\n            </span>\n            <h2 className=\"text-[28px] sm:text-[38px] font-bold text-white tracking-tight mt-2\">\n              Garage-to-Factory Progression Model\n            </h2>\n            <p className=\"mt-4 text-[14.5px] text-white/60 font-light leading-[1.6]\">\n              Our proprietary process designed to bring enterprise AI concepts from rapid proof-of-concept simulation into dedicated high-availability operations.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n\n          <div className=\"relative border border-white/5 bg-[#030304]/30 rounded-[32px] p-6 lg:p-12 overflow-hidden\">\n            <div className=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-[50%] aspect-square bg-[#009DFF]/2 rounded-full blur-[80px]\" />\n            \n            <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 relative z-10\">\n              {/* Phase 1 */}\n              <div className=\"flex flex-col justify-between p-6 rounded-[20px] bg-black/40 border border-white/5 hover:border-[#E4000F]/20 transition-all duration-300\">\n                <div>\n                  <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between\">\n                    <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono font-bold text-[#E4000F]\">PHASE 01</span>\n                    <span className=\"px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-[9px] font-mono bg-[#E4000F]/10 text-[#E4000F] border border-[#E4000F]/20 uppercase\">Incubation</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <h4 className=\"text-[18px] font-bold text-white mt-4\">The GFF Garage</h4>\n                  <p className=\"mt-2.5 text-[12.5px] leading-[1.5] text-white/50 font-light\">\n                    The starting point where engineering architects design sandbox blueprints, calculate strict technical readiness, evaluate custom model configurations, and validate feasibility within a low-stakes environment.\n                  </p>\n                </div>\n                <div className=\"mt-6 pt-4 border-t border-white/5\">\n                  <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase\">Deliverables</span>\n                  <div className=\"mt-1 flex flex-wrap gap-1\">\n                    <span className=\"px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-white/5 text-[9.5px] text-white/70\">Custom Blueprint</span>\n                    <span className=\"px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-white/5 text-[9.5px] text-white/70\">ROI Feasibility Model</span>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Phase 2 */}\n              <div className=\"flex flex-col justify-between p-6 rounded-[20px] bg-black/40 border border-white/5 hover:border-violet-500/20 transition-all duration-300\">\n                <div>\n                  <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between\">\n                    <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono font-bold text-violet-400\">PHASE 02</span>\n                    <span className=\"px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-[9px] font-mono bg-violet-500/10 text-violet-400 border border-violet-500/20 uppercase\">Hardening</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <h4 className=\"text-[18px] font-bold text-white mt-4\">The GFF Foundry</h4>\n                  <p className=\"mt-2.5 text-[12.5px] leading-[1.5] text-white/50 font-light\">\n                    High-end assembly stage. Here we take approved configurations and build out vector DB schemas, implement robust compliance guardrails, bind APIs, construct knowledge networks, and deploy fully isolated systems.\n                  </p>\n                </div>\n                <div className=\"mt-6 pt-4 border-t border-white/5\">\n                  <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase\">Deliverables</span>\n                  <div className=\"mt-1 flex flex-wrap gap-1\">\n                    <span className=\"px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-white/5 text-[9.5px] text-white/70\">Hardened Sandboxes</span>\n                    <span className=\"px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-white/5 text-[9.5px] text-white/70\">Compliance Guardrails</span>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Phase 3 */}\n              <div className=\"flex flex-col justify-between p-6 rounded-[20px] bg-black/40 border border-white/5 hover:border-[#009DFF]/20 transition-all duration-300\">\n                <div>\n                  <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between\">\n                    <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono font-bold text-[#009DFF]\">PHASE 03</span>\n                    <span className=\"px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-[9px] font-mono bg-[#009DFF]/10 text-[#009DFF] border border-[#009DFF]/20 uppercase\">Continuous Ops</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <h4 className=\"text-[18px] font-bold text-white mt-4\">The GFF Factory</h4>\n                  <p className=\"mt-2.5 text-[12.5px] leading-[1.5] text-white/50 font-light\">\n                    Continuous operational execution. Scale multi-agent loops with 24/7 SLA monitoring, implement model-fine-tuning cron cycles, secure cost curves, and optimize telemetry reporting in production.\n                  </p>\n                </div>\n                <div className=\"mt-6 pt-4 border-t border-white/5\">\n                  <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase\">Deliverables</span>\n                  <div className=\"mt-1 flex flex-wrap gap-1\">\n                    <span className=\"px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-white/5 text-[9.5px] text-white/70\">Autonomous Clusters</span>\n                    <span className=\"px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-white/5 text-[9.5px] text-white/70\">24/7 Performance Ops</span>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      {/* SECTION 5: RELATED PLATFORMS */}\n      <section className=\"relative w-full px-6 lg:px-16 pb-24 border-t border-white/5 pt-20\">\n        <div className=\"max-w-[1795px] mx-auto\">\n          <div className=\"text-center max-w-[800px] mx-auto mb-16\">\n            <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono tracking-[0.2em] text-[#009DFF] uppercase font-bold\">\n              PLATFORM ECOSYSTEM\n            </span>\n            <h2 className=\"text-[28px] sm:text-[38px] font-bold text-white tracking-tight mt-2\">\n              Related Platforms & Interfaces\n            </h2>\n            <p className=\"mt-4 text-[14.5px] text-white/60 font-light leading-[1.6]\">\n              Our underlying technology is distributed across core platforms designed to operationalize capabilities in real-time.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n\n          <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6\">\n            <a \n              href=\"/platforms\" \n              className=\"group p-6 rounded-[20px] border border-white/5 bg-[#030304]/60 backdrop-blur-[8px] hover:border-[#009DFF]/30 transition-all\"\n            >\n              <h4 className=\"text-[16px] font-semibold text-white tracking-tight group-hover:text-[#009DFF] transition-colors flex items-center justify-between\">\n                <span>The Platform Spec</span>\n                <ArrowRight className=\"w-4 h-4 text-white/40 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\" />\n              </h4>\n              <p className=\"mt-2.5 text-[12.5px] leading-[1.5] text-white/50 font-light\">\n                Browse our complete system architecture specifications, integration endpoints, and enterprise-grade host layouts.\n              </p>\n            </a>\n\n            <a \n              href=\"/platforms/foundry\" \n              className=\"group p-6 rounded-[20px] border border-white/5 bg-[#030304]/60 backdrop-blur-[8px] hover:border-[#E4000F]/30 transition-all\"\n            >\n              <h4 className=\"text-[16px] font-semibold text-white tracking-tight group-hover:text-[#E4000F] transition-colors flex items-center justify-between\">\n                <span>GFF Foundry</span>\n                <ArrowRight className=\"w-4 h-4 text-white/40 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\" />\n              </h4>\n              <p className=\"mt-2.5 text-[12.5px] leading-[1.5] text-white/50 font-light\">\n                Deploy sandboxes, map custom data ingestion pipelines, and bind multi-modal agent endpoints in a secure interface.\n              </p>\n            </a>\n\n            <a \n              href=\"/build/sandbox\" \n              className=\"group p-6 rounded-[20px] border border-white/5 bg-[#030304]/60 backdrop-blur-[8px] hover:border-purple-500/30 transition-all\"\n            >\n              <h4 className=\"text-[16px] font-semibold text-white tracking-tight group-hover:text-purple-400 transition-colors flex items-center justify-between\">\n                <span>Enterprise Sandbox</span>\n                <ArrowRight className=\"w-4 h-4 text-white/40 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\" />\n              </h4>\n              <p className=\"mt-2.5 text-[12.5px] leading-[1.5] text-white/50 font-light\">\n                Launch interactive AI simulations, test prompts, select foundation layers, and calculate compliance bounds instantly.\n              </p>\n            </a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      {/* Premium CTA */}\n      <div className=\"max-w-[1795px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-16 pb-24\">\n        <PremiumCTA\n          title=\"Ready to Scale Your Autonomous Core?\"\n          description=\"Schedule a structural session with our Lead Systems Architects to model custom agent pipelines and secure integration paths tailored for your stack.\"\n          primaryLabel=\"Consult Systems Architect\"\n          secondaryLabel=\"Inspect Platform Spec\"\n        />\n      </div>\n    </InnerPageShell>\n  );\n}\n"}}}
